  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed erection of a first floor rear extension by reason of its depth and protrusion beyond the established rear building line at first floor level would introduce an incongruous form of development visually harming the host building and the visual consistency of the rear elevation of the terrace.  The proposed development is therefore considered contrary to policies 7.4 and 7.8 of the London Plan 2011, policy CS9 (Protecting and Enhancing Islington’s Built and Historic Environment) of Islington’s Core Strategy 2011, policies D4 (Designing in context), D11 (Alterations and extensions) of Islington's Unitary Development Plan 2002, emerging policy DM1 (Design) of Islington’s Development Policies Document Submission Version 2012, and Islington's Urban Design Guide (2006)."
